content.rendered:
The Maldives Rattan Outdoor Tub Chair is made with a flat Polyethylene Resin weave for ultimate strength and integrity. 

With a welded aluminium frame it can be left outside all year round.

These can be stacked up to 2 high.

With many related products you can have a complete look running throughout your venue.

Usually held in stock for a 3-5 working day delivery.

Contract grade furniture.

All prices are subject to VAT.
